Text:
There are 66 fries in a pound of fries

If they were to borrow Starbucks' policy, each week MacDonald's would give one pound of fries to each of its 1.9M employees

This would amount to 6.5B fries per year--a small fraction of the 217 trillion fries $MCD sells each and every year
